<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head lang="ru">
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Ландшафтный дизайн</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
        <style>
            *{
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            }
            body {
                background-color: #f7f9f7;
                color: #1e2a1e;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }
            .container {
                max-width: 1300px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 0 40px;
            }
            .selection-title {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                letter-spacing: -0.02em;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
                color:#1a3b2e;
                position: relative;
            }
            .selection-title:after {
                content: '';
                display: block;
                width: 70px;
                height: 4px;
                background: #6f9e7c;
                margin-top: 8px;
            }
            .green-accent {
                color: #2b5e3b;
            }
            .hero-header {
                background-color: #ffffff;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #dde5da;
                padding: 25px 0 15px;
            }
            .hero-header .container{
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .main-headline {
                font-size: 3rem;
                font-weight: 300;
                color: #1a3b2e;
                line-height: 1.1;
            }
            .main-headline strong{
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #1f4d2f;
                display: block;
                font-size: 3.8rem;
            }
            .subheadline {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
                color: #4b6b4f;
                margin-top: 5px;
                font-weight: 400;
            }
            .feature-grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
                gap: 30px;
                margin: 50px 0 40px;
            }
            .feature-card {
                background: white;
                padding: 30px 25px;
                box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 20, 0, 0.03);
                border-radius: 4px;
                border-top: 6px solid #8ab893;
            }
            .feature-card h3 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: #1a3b2e;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
            .feature-card p {
                color: #2f422f;
                font-size: 1rem;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }
            .lighting-block {
                background: #eaf0e9;
                padding: 45px 40px;
                margin: 40px 0;
                border-left: 8px solid #5a8767;
            }
            .lighting-block h2 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
                font-weight: 650;
                color: #1a3424;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            .lighting-block p {
                max-width: 800px;
                color: #2e402e;
                margin-bottom: 12px;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            .eco-block {
                background: #3b5e4a;
                color: white;
                padding: 40px;
                text-align: center;
                margin: 40px 0;
                border-radius: 4px;
            }
            .eco-block h2 {
                font-size: 2.6rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
            }
            .eco-block p {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                opacity: 0.9;
                font-style: italic;
                margin-top: 15px;
            }
            .extra-results {
                background: #f5f3eb;
                padding: 20px 30px;
                margin: 30px 0;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: 400;
                border: 1px dashed #8faa8a;
                color: #2b4b2b;
            }
            .popular-services {
                background: white;
                padding: 50px 0;
                margin: 30px 0;
            }
            .popular-header {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: baseline;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .popular-header h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: 650;
                color: #1d3b2a;
            }
            .popular-tags {
                display: flex;
                gap: 30px;
            }
            .popular-tags span {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                background: #eef5ea;
                padding: 6px 18px;
                border-radius: 40px;
                color: #23542f;
            }
            .project-cards {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
                gap: 20px;
                margin: 40px 0;
            }
            .project-item {
                background: #f8faf8;
                padding: 20px;
                border: 1px solid #cbd8cd;
            }
            .project-item .title {
                font-weight: 700;
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                color: #163f21;
                margin-bottom: 3px;
            }
            .project-item .location {
                color: #4f6b55;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }
            .water-features {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
                gap: 25px;
                margin: 60px 0;
            }
            .water-col {
                background: white;
                padding: 30px 25px;
                border-bottom:  4px solid #7dab86;
            }
            .water-col h3 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: #1a4227;
                margin-bottom: 25px;
            }
            .water-col ul {
                list-style: none;
            }
            .water-col li {
                margin-bottom: 12px;
                font-size: 1.05rem;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 8px;
                color: #283f2b;
            }
            .water-col li i {
                color: #527a5c;
                width: 20px;
            }
            .greening-block {
                margin: 40px 0 60px;
            }
            .greening-header {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #1b472b;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            .greening-grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
                gap: 30px;
            }
            .greening-card {
                background: #edf4ec;
                padding: 30px;
                border-radius: 2px;
            }
            .greening-card ul {
                list-style: none;
            }
            .greening-card li {
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                color: #1d3b25;
            }
            .questions-block {
                background: #fff;
                border: 2px solid #bdd3bd;
                padding: 50px;
                text-align: center;
                margin: 40px 0;
            }
            .questions-block h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                color: #1d3b24;
            }
            .questions-block p {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                color: #3e603e;
                margin-top: 15px;
            }
            .slogan-block {
                background: #1c3423;
                color: white;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 50px;
                font-size: 2.8rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                line-height: 1.3;
                margin: 30px 0;
            }
            .slogan-block small {
                display: block;
                font-size: 1.3rem;
                font-weight: 300;
                margin-top: 15px;
                color: #d0e2cf;
            }
            .stats-grid {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-around;
                background: #f0f6ef;
                padding: 40px;
                margin: 40px 0;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 30px;
            }
            .stat-item {
                text-align: center;
            }
            .stat-number {
                font-size: 4.2rem;
                font-weight: 800;
                color: #1e4a2a;
                line-height: 1;
            }
            .stat-label {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
                color: #2b472b;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 0.5rem;
            }
            .completed-projects {
                background: #e3eae1;
                padding: 50px 40px;
                margin: 50px 0;
            }
            .completed-projects h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
                color: #103118;
            }
            .completed-projects .task {
                padding: 1.3rem;
                color: #29462f;
                margin-top: 10px;
                max-width: 600px;
            }
            .footer-note {
                background: #fff;
                padding: 25px;
                border-top: 2px solid #bdcfbd;
                text-align: right;
                font-size: 1rem;
                color: #2a4c2a;
            }
            hr {
                border: none;
                border-top: 2px solid #cbdccb;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            .anchor {
                display: block;
                position: relative;
                top: -20px;
                visibility: hidden;
            }
            .image-placeholder {
                background: #cbdccb;
                height: 140px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                color: #2c4f39;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                border-radius: 2px;
                background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 10px 10px, #a7bca7 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to right, #b5ceb8, #d1e2d0);
                background-size: 20px 20px, cover;
            }
            @media (max-width: 900px) {
                .feature-grid, .project-cards, .water-features, .greening-grid {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                }
                .container {padding: 0 20px;}
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="anchor" id="proektirovanie">
        </div>
        <div class="anchor" id="blagoustoistvo">
        </div>
        <div class="anchor" id="gazon">
        </div>

        <div class="hero-header">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="main-headline">
                    Ландшафтный дизайн
                <strong>Ландшафтный дизайн</strong>
                </h1>
                <div class="subheadline">Благоустройство и озеленение участника</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <h3>ПРОЕКТИРОВАНИЕ</h3>
                <p>Предоставление готового проекта в течении 3 дня</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>БЛАГОУСТРОЙСТВО И ОЗЕЛЕНЕНИЕ УЧАСТКА</h3>
                <p>Работы, осмотр, бордюры и монтаж</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>УСТРОЙСТВО ГАЗОНА</h3>
                <p>Выбор растений, подтесов участка, посев и осмотр</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="eco-block">
                <h2>ЭКОЛОГИЧНЫЙ КОМПЛЕКСНЫЙ ПОДХОД</h2>
                <p>От идеи до ухода</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="extra-results">
                <p>ДОПОЛНИТЕЛЬНЫЕ РЕЗУЛЬТАТЫ Изменения на участке</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
